reviewText: I bought this for myself, and then purchased it again as a gift for someone who thought they'd seen just about everything on WWII.  She was pleasantly surprised at the documentary on the contribution Hollywood made to the war effort.  The movies are very old, but I would buy this again.
Great Blu-Ray Pack with 3 good movies. I Got it on sale and loved all 3 films. no disappointments here. Pick it up give it a go if your into war films
